==English==

===Noun===
'''[[whoopie]] [[cushion]]'''

# A small, [[rubber]] [[bag]] with a [[flap]] used as a [[practical joke]] device, usually for flatulence humor. The bag is filled with [[air]] and placed on a seat where the unsuspecting [[victim]] will sit; once he/she sits on the device, the bag deflates and make a sound similar to one [[pass gas|passing gas]].